msgid ""
"Keep in mind that section and property names can't contain spaces. "
"Anything after a space will be ignored on save and on load."
msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_configfile.rst:47
msgid ""
"ConfigFiles can also contain manually written comment lines starting with"
" a semicolon (``;``). Those lines will be ignored when parsing the file. "
"Note that comments will be lost when saving the ConfigFile. This can "
"still be useful for dedicated server configuration files, which are "
"typically never overwritten without explicit user action."
